Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:06.88,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1920,0)}Lord Jeremiah, how does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.95,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting in the Deputy Governor-General's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:12.49,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,What bad manners. Your background will be exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:18.01,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1040)}Well, Lord Jeremiah, my lineage differs from yours anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.37,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.83,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Once the revolution undertaken by the Purist Faction is complete, {ni wa}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.89,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I'll submit a proposal for you to become a baroness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.26,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Baroness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:31.12,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Not some imitation like a Knight, which lasts for only one generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:35.05,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,True nobility that your descendants get to inherit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:35.76,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.93,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is Kururugi Suzaku's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.97,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the details of the parade to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:46.61,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I've already checked and arranged everything from the coordination of the television stations to which route to take to the courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.77,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,I've established counter-sniper measures as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.02,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.94,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I must not be shamed any further than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:57.06,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Twice I've allowed members of the royal family to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:57.76,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:00.45,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.30,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first mission I had as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:05.70,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I was assigned as a guard at the Aries Imperial Villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:08.95,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Aries Imperial Villa... Eight years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.45,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, Queen Marianne was...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:11.71,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:16.74,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the orders from above, a minimal number of guards was placed on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:20.26,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, we weren't able to prevent rebels from penetrating our defenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.74,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first setback I faced...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:32.44,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I was a man who'd never known failure since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.32,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I was then posted to Area 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:40.74,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,The place where Queen Marianne's orphans, Prince Lelouch and Princess Nunnally, lost their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:44.95,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,And now... even Prince Clovis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.71,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.76,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness Clovis... Queen Marianne...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:55.67,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Please laugh at the useless me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.89,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.39,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.47,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Please wipe away your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.48,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, it isn't like you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.34,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That's true I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:11.90,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,The way I am now, even my sister, Lilycia, would laugh at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:17.15,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm a man from the noble Earl Gottwald's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:21.12,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I shall avenge His Highness Clovis and regain our former honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.72,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Viletta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:24.42,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:29.48,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take hold and seize the future with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.05,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a Knight of One, the personal sword of His Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.61,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.94,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm Jeremiah Gottwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.45,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah,{\alpha&HFF&} why!?{\alpha&H00&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:49.08,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jeremiah, why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.21,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.{\alpha&HFF&} Relay this to the entire army. {Alpha time to chunk to match the screen I guess...} {\alpha&H00&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.33,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Relay this to the entire army. {Alpha time to chunk to match the screen I guess...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.75,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go,{\alpha&HFF&} with as much effort as you can!{\alpha&H00&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.61,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go, with as much effort as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.50,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go, with all your effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:02.68,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,This is a direct order from me, Margrave Jeremiah Gottwald!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.73,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go, with all your effort!
